Package: caractr
Title: Additional functions to deal with character vectors
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Stéphane Le Hénanff", "Stéphane Le Hénanff", email = "github@le-henanff.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: caractr provides a few functions in addition of those within stringr package.
    Its name corresponds to the simplified French translation of character because some of the functions deal with French characters.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.5)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports:
    dplyr,
    glue,
    purrr,
    readr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    stats
